										"paragraphStyle" : {
											"__type" : "textStyle"
										},
										"string" : "Let's see what a Repository instance contains. The full name of the repo would be more useful to display. But how can we access it? We open a playground on the repo and get the name from the raw data. As before, we extract this code as a method, this time called “fullName”. Now let's use this in our Repositories view. We can now browse the list of repos."
